Also 32bit vs 64bit might be a problem, this stackoverflow post lists various causes for this error message.

body:
Which python version is pip3 linked to? You mentioned installing 3.5 AND 3.6. Maybe you're trying to install the tensorflow version for python3.5 while pip3 links to python3.6

Also  32bit vs 64bit might be a problem, [this](http://stackoverflow.com/questions/28568070/filename-whl-is-not-supported-wheel-on-this-platform) stackoverflow post lists various causes for this error message.
